#            isPalin()  = O(n)  worst case ek baar aur traverse
#            Total      = O(n) + O(n) = O(n)
#
#  Space →  O(1)
#            Sirf pointers use kiye — koi extra array/string nahi
#            Only pointers used — no extra array or string slicing
#            (String slicing s[l+1:r] would be O(n) space — avoided)
