#  ONE LINE TO REMEMBER
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
#  Pehle mismatch pe → left hatao ya right hatao → dono try karo
#  At first mismatch → skip left or skip right → try BOTH
#  Agar dono mein se ek bhi palindrome → True
#  If either gives a palindrome → True
#  Dono fail → False
#  Both fail → False
#
